{"tid":2035661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Space X創辦人Elon Musk兒命名「X Æ A-12」？母親透露新名字","createTime":"2020-05-26T05:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T17:39:18.000Z","uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"71e61da0830d89d16d0aa0fa129bb73374e92afa","tid":2035661,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/26/phpwdlfVo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2FphpwdlfVo.jpg&h=16f886d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬斯克（左）與女友葛萊姆絲（右）近日誕下一子。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2020-05-26 08:14:40<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕電動車大廠特斯拉、太空公司Space X創辦人馬斯克（Elon Musk）與加拿大歌手葛萊姆絲（Grimes）日前喜獲麟兒，行事風格特殊的兩人，決定將兒子取名為「X &AElig; A-12 Musk」，讓外界一頭霧水，且不符合當地法規。被問到是否改名？葛萊姆絲簡短回應「X &AElig; A-Xii」。<br />\n<br />\n葛萊姆絲先前向外界解釋，X代表未知變數、&AElig;意味愛與人工智慧、A-12則是SR-17（應為SR-71）黑鳥偵察機前身，也是兩人喜歡的飛機，沒有武器、防衛，只有速度、善戰，卻非暴力。此外，A也包含她的愛歌大天使（Archangel）。<br />\n<br />\n雖然兒子的姓名意涵豐富，但兩人居住地美國加州政府規定，姓名須從26個字母中組成，不得使用象形、表意文字或變音符號。<br />\n<br />\n有網友在葛萊姆絲最新的一篇IG貼文中問道，「你們有因為加州的法律更改兒子的姓名嗎？新名字是什麼？」葛萊姆絲回覆「X &AElig; A-Xii」，並補充說「老實說，羅馬數字看起來更棒」，但沒有說明改名的原因。"},{"pid":"56b3c9bc0b0872fbd330322a1097ba2a46456215","tid":2035661,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"MK. II"},{"pid":"840538964d3cfc67a4b6921e8bebb3efb462c07e","tid":2035661,"uid":312242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"X &AElig; A-<span style=\"color: red;\">Xi</span>i"},{"pid":"442e07fa0e4fdcd7db5235dd41fbe1d9355425df","tid":2035661,"uid":34714,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"玩鳩個仔😭"},{"pid":"087cd6f10dd7085070e27938647598bf3e86a61c","tid":2035661,"uid":310399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"c932fafc6aac6d835b92f2ca7ac0354a3dc48ac7","tid":2035661,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊個話要結婚先生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8bd36eaa6e01f4743a28109bd3951299969cd9a0","tid":2035661,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqbtUgy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqbtUgy.png&h=ae7770e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edb721ec77395f0099a881564d697b61f0fa1920","tid":2035661,"uid":34395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"&AElig; 點讀？一個字定兩個字？"},{"pid":"2e1d62352504f6f5d070ed9a6db04ac4e45612e3","tid":2035661,"uid":20241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"442e07fa0e4fdcd7db5235dd41fbe1d9355425df","tid":2035661,"uid":34714,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"玩鳩個仔😭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"唔要個首抽就拎嚟，我俾佢玩多10次都制"},{"pid":"882926594c55f3ef1b1bfd59d75c6c6ef2e65a06","tid":2035661,"uid":34395,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"442e07fa0e4fdcd7db5235dd41fbe1d9355425df","tid":2035661,"uid":34714,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"玩鳩個仔😭"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"做到elon musk 個仔叫咩都無所謂啦"},{"pid":"c45416cac858b66e12c2e3498ba133d204728d70","tid":2035661,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"加州政府話哩個名唔比reg要改過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527bac4443588d7b63cc67563919301e1193596e","tid":2035661,"uid":89857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"edb721ec77395f0099a881564d697b61f0fa1920","tid":2035661,"uid":34395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"&AElig; 點讀？一個字定兩個字？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"Anaheim Electronics<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1c8f70c1c55ee8b0d3029f5e3fb9726b0682a2","tid":2035661,"uid":43041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"日本山梨縣甲府市就讀高中三年級的學生赤池肇，原本被母親取名為「王子様」（日文，王子殿下的意思），害他從小到大一路都被旁人言語霸凌，15歲那年想改名還受到大力反對，好不容易熬到今年2月才偷偷向法院提出改名的申請，並在本月5日獲准，讓他忍不住在推特開心報喜，「我要切斷過去的感情，展開新的生活！」<br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，已經高中三年級的赤池肇即將步入大學生活，但尚未改名之前，他可是過著天天被人嘲笑的生活，「曾被第一次見面的人嘲諷，辦KTV的會員卡也被質疑是不是真名，甚至連去買東西還會被陌生人調侃，『哦，是王子殿下』，實在很羞愧。」<br />\n<br />\n然而，赤池肇一直忍到15歲終於受不了，向父母提出改名的要求，卻受到母親大力反對，現在雙親離婚，他遞交改名申請獲得法院准許，母親就算再不願意也沒辦法，「因為我想在上大學前改變這樣的生活。」<br />\n<br />\n赤池肇本月7日在自己的推特上公開改名成功的事，並PO出相關文件證明，「我經歷了一段悲慘的人生，現在我想切斷過去的感情，開始展開我的新生活！」同時也希望透過自己的例子，鼓勵那些同樣被父母取了怪名字而感到痛苦的人，勇敢站出來爭取自己的權益，人生就會變得很不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n至於赤池肇的母親離婚後已經再嫁，她得知兒子改名以及背後的慘痛經歷後，也感到相當抱歉。而赤池肇僅半開玩笑地表示，如果母親生了弟弟，希望不要再取這種讓人困擾的怪名字了。"},{"pid":"7a1f6434260a1d1f438cd2efc8344d277d0840ff","tid":2035661,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"幾多核心？<br />\n<br />\n用咩避震？<br />\n<br />\n有冇隱身塗層？"},{"pid":"3f6d8d1164d9b35bee08cb7bb5849e2e5502427f","tid":2035661,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"發生於西元2000年(平成12年)的「鼎殺父事件」。起因父親將兒子取名為「鼎」（日語為かなえ，較為少用），但這個名字被周圍的人認為是奇怪的名字且偏向女性化，兒子因而被人愚弄，兒子成年之後改了名字，但事情沒有因為兒子改了名字而結束。2000年9月，發生了這名兒子殺害命名父親的事件。有証言指出：被告者在法庭上從法官的話語中第一次得知了自己名字的深遠內涵，鼎在中國古代天子在位時代表具有重大地位身分之義。雖然是個好名字卻因為周圍的人都不了解涵義所在，因此被當作DQN名字看待而遭人愚弄，遺憾地發展成殺人事件。"},{"pid":"343a90fdc857416670a65cf30598a74b7039e7a0","tid":2035661,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"日後遺傳老豆知識<br />\nIron man 不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673112a8abf886cd13774c2438e2d70dd1571fb8","tid":2035661,"uid":131188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"諗起呢張, 搵2下仲搵到已經有人整左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/facebook/001/846/081/8fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Ffacebook%2F001%2F846%2F081%2F8fa.jpg&h=7504cdd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f087f5d96ea11e6bb558e464d15f594797cc2442","tid":2035661,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"882926594c55f3ef1b1bfd59d75c6c6ef2e65a06","tid":2035661,"uid":34395,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"442e07fa0e4fdcd7db5235dd41fbe1d9355425df","tid":2035661,"uid":34714,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"玩鳩個仔😭"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"做到elon musk 個仔叫咩都無所謂啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/green-24_i6knM_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fgreen-24_i6knM_1200x0.png&h=8b439da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁又係啊 一出世就可以靠daddy拎到張中国綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c6148d7f8374662d925a545c8139c0a4c995da","tid":2035661,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"edb721ec77395f0099a881564d697b61f0fa1920","tid":2035661,"uid":34395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"&AElig; 點讀？一個字定兩個字？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05